  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个Aurelia项目的沟通流程图，核心是项目经理这个角色，他向上对接NFWB的工作人员，向下管理各个专业负责人。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "PM",
        "NFWB",
        "TECH"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，项目经理是枢纽。那NFWB staff和项目经理之间是什么关系？是单向汇报还是双向沟通？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "NFWB",
        "PM"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "是双向的，NFWB staff和项目经理互相沟通。专业负责人那边也是双向的，项目经理统筹技术团队。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "NFWB",
        "PM",
        "TECH"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我把NFWB staff放在左边，项目经理居中，技术负责人在项目经理右侧，用双向箭头连接。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "NFWB",
        "PM",
        "TECH"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "对了，项目经理还需要对外协调几个关键方：居民代表、警消应急部门，还有NYSDEC州环保厅。这些是单向输出还是双向？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "PM",
        "RES",
        "EMG",
        "NYSDEC"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "居民那边应该是双向吧？需要收集反馈。警消和NYSDEC呢，是项目经理主动联络他们，还是他们也可能找过来？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "PM",
        "RES",
        "EMG",
        "NYSDEC"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "实际运作中，这三方都是项目经理主动去协调对接的，用单向箭头比较合适，强调PM的统筹职能。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "PM",
        "RES",
        "EMG",
        "NYSDEC"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "明白了，从项目经理拉出三条单向线，分别指向Residents、Police and fire、还有NYSDEC。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "PM",
        "RES",
        "EMG",
        "NYSDEC"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "等等，NFWB和PM之间的箭头方向我再确认一下——是NFWB指向PM，还是互相指向？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "NFWB",
        "PM"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "我检查一下，刚才画的是NFWB指向PM的单向箭头，但您说是双向沟通。我改成双向箭头，同时PM和TECH之间也保持双向。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "NFWB",
        "PM",
        "TECH"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 11,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，这样准确。NFWB staff和项目经理是平级协作关系，专业负责人也是双向汇报机制。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "NFWB",
        "PM",
        "TECH"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 12,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "调整完成。现在布局是：NFWB staff在左，项目经理居中，技术负责人在PM右侧；PM下方分出三条单向线到居民、警消和NYSDEC。整体从左到右的流向。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "NFWB",
        "PM",
        "TECH",
        "RES",
        "EMG",
        "NYSDEC"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 13,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "完美，这个结构清晰展示了Aurelia项目的沟通层级。项目经理确实是整个协调网络的核心节点。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "PM",
        "NFWB",
        "TECH",
        "RES",
        "EMG",
        "NYSDEC"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    }
